---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Image-based Payload Yaw Control"
  lang="en"
>
  <main>

    <section class="hero">

        <p class="hero-subtitle">
            Demonstration using Reinforcement Learning,
            Image-based Pose Estimation,
            and Raspberry Pi
        </p>
        <h2>
            Image-based Payload Yaw Control
        </h2>

        <p class="hero-text">
            The system estimates payload orientation from camera images
            and automatically controls the yaw angle
            using four thrusters.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-video">
        <video controls muted playsinline preload="metadata">
          <source
          src={`${base}/videos/With_Without_Control-Raspberry_Pi.mp4`}
          type="video/mp4"
          />
          お使いのブラウザは動画再生に対応していません。
        </video>

        <p class="hero-caption">
          This demonstration shows real-time payload yaw control on Raspberry Pi
          using yaw angles estimated from camera images.
          The left shows the proposed control system, while the right shows the same conditions without control.
        </p>
        </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-video {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .hero-video video {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  .hero-caption {
    width: min(100%, 760px);
    margin: 12px auto 0;
    text-align: left;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #555;
  }
</style>